<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.10.10">
<l>vāvit taṭañcūḻ maṇimut tāṟṟu naṟaiyūr neṭumālai</l>
<l>nāvil paravi neñcil koṇṭu nampi nāmattai</l>
<l>kāvit taṭaṅkaṇ maṭavār kēḷvaṉ kaliya ṉolimālai</l>
<l>mēvic colla vallār pāvam nillā vīyumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[For] those who are able to learn and recite [this] garland of words of Kaliyaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">the darling of ladies with wide eyes [like] dark lotuses,</l>
<l>About the name of the noble, keeping [it] in [his] heart</l>
<l rend="indent">and extolling [it] on his tongue,</l>
<l>About tall Māl of Naṟaiyūr on a river with jewels and pearls,</l>
<l>Surrounded by stepwells and pools, sins will vanish without delay.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
